@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.Localization
@inject IHtmlLocalizer<SharedResource> L
@model GrcMvc.Models.ViewModels.VerifyMfaViewModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = L["Auth_VerifyMfa"].Value;
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <div class="card shadow-lg border-0">
                <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white text-center py-4">
                    <i class="bi bi-shield-lock fs-1"></i>
                    <h4 class="mb-0 mt-2">@L["Auth_VerifyMfa"]</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <p class="text-muted text-center mb-4">
                        @L["Auth_VerificationCodeSent"]<br/>
                        <strong>@Model.MaskedEmail</strong>
                    </p>

                    <form asp-action="VerifyMfa" method="post" id="mfaForm">
                        <input type="hidden" asp-for="ReturnUrl" />
                        <input type="hidden" asp-for="RememberMe" />
                        
                        <div asp-validation-summary="ModelOnly" class="alert alert-danger" role="alert"></div>

                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <label asp-for="Code" class="form-label">@L["Auth_VerificationCode"]</label>
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2" id="codeInputs">
                                @for (int i = 0; i < 6; i++)
                                {
                                    <input type="text" 
                                           class="form-control text-center fs-3 code-input" 
                                           maxlength="1" 
                                           pattern="[0-9]"
                                           inputmode="numeric"
                                           style="width: 50px; height: 60px;" 
                                           data-index="@i" />
                                }
                            </div>
                            <input type="hidden" asp-for="Code" id="fullCode" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="Code" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="d-grid gap-2 mb-3">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                                <i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> @L["Auth_Verify"]
                            </button>
                        </div>

                        <div class="text-center">
                            <p class="text-muted mb-2">
                                <i class="bi bi-clock"></i> 
                                @L["Auth_CodeValidFor"] <span id="countdown" class="fw-bold text-primary">10:00</span>
                            </p>
                            <a href="#" id="resendCode" class="text-decoration-none disabled-link">
                                <i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat"></i> @L["Auth_ResendCode"]
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer bg-light text-center py-3">
                    <small class="text-muted">
                        <i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i> 
                        @L["Auth_AccountProtectionPriority"]
                    </small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@section Scripts {
    <partial name="_ValidationScriptsPartial" />
    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            const inputs = document.querySelectorAll('.code-input');
            const fullCodeInput = document.getElementById('fullCode');
            
            // Auto-focus first input
            inputs[0].focus();
            
            // Handle input
            inputs.forEach((input, index) => {
                input.addEventListener('input', function(e) {
                    const value = e.target.value;
                    
                    // Only allow numbers
                    if (!/^\d*$/.test(value)) {
                        e.target.value = '';
                        return;
                    }
                    
                    // Move to next input
                    if (value && index < inputs.length - 1) {
                        inputs[index + 1].focus();
                    }
                    
                    // Update hidden input
                    updateFullCode();
                });
                
                input.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
                    // Move to previous input on backspace
                    if (e.key === 'Backspace' && !e.target.value && index > 0) {
                        inputs[index - 1].focus();
                    }
                });
                
                // Handle paste
                input.addEventListener('paste', function(e) {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    const pastedData = e.clipboardData.getData('text').replace(/\D/g, '').slice(0, 6);
                    
                    pastedData.split('').forEach((char, i) => {
                        if (inputs[i]) {
                            inputs[i].value = char;
                        }
                    });
                    
                    updateFullCode();
                    
                    // Focus last filled or next empty
                    const lastIndex = Math.min(pastedData.length, inputs.length - 1);
                    inputs[lastIndex].focus();
                });
            });
            
            function updateFullCode() {
                let code = '';
                inputs.forEach(input => {
                    code += input.value;
                });
                fullCodeInput.value = code;
            }
            
            // Countdown timer
            let timeLeft = 10 * 60; // 10 minutes
            const countdownEl = document.getElementById('countdown');
            const resendLink = document.getElementById('resendCode');
            
            const timer = setInterval(function() {
                timeLeft--;
                
                const minutes = Math.floor(timeLeft / 60);
                const seconds = timeLeft % 60;
                countdownEl.textContent = `${minutes}:${seconds.toString().padStart(2, '0')}`;
                
                if (timeLeft <= 0) {
                    clearInterval(timer);
                    countdownEl.textContent = window.L ? window.L('Auth_Expired') : 'Expired';
                    countdownEl.classList.remove('text-primary');
                    countdownEl.classList.add('text-danger');
                    resendLink.classList.remove('disabled-link');
                }
            }, 1000);
        });
    </script>
    <style>
        .code-input:focus {
            border-color: #0d6efd;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.25rem rgba(13, 110, 253, 0.25);
        }
        .disabled-link {
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }
    </style>
}
